TableContextTimeStampAfterTable: {29242=Orca has a track record of over 20 years as a leading sports apparel brand, predominantly in the triathlon arena. Just as the triathlon embodies endurance, stamina and versatility, so does every piece in the Orca collection. Working tirelessly over the past two decades to evolve, innovate and perform with their athletes, today Orca is recognized as the preferred brand amongst new entrant and professional triathletes around the globe.In 1992, founder and former triathlon champion, Scott Unsworth, set up Performance Speedsuits Ltd in his native New Zealand, spurred by a passion to create better, faster wetsuits than those on the market. Three years later, Performance Speedsuits was renamed and the Orca brand emerged. Since the late 90s, Orca has been a trusted companion to swimmers, runners and cyclists around the world with their organic designs and a firm focus on performance. The knowledge and expertise of their athletes shapes their research and nourishes the development of their products. Go further, faster, with Orca.}
